DESIGN, EVALUATION, AND APPLICAION OF HEART RATE VARIABILITY ANALYSIS SOFTWARE (HRVAS) by John T. Ramshur
A Thesis Submitted in Partial Fulfillment of the
Requirements for the Degree of Master of Science
Major: Biomedical Engineering
The University of Memphis August 2010

Acknowledgements
